OL,4,G1600FTrucking Heavy
OL,5,     GIn Wales, haulier Ian gears
OL,6,     Ghimself up for a major cross-
OL,7,     Gcountry mega-move that requires a
OL,8,     Gpolice escort. And in Hull, mega
OL,9,     Gmover Steve is in charge of
OL,10,     Gshifting a 38-tonne screener.
OL,11,G1700FTraffic Cops
OL,12,     GA young speeder crashes
OL,13,     Gspectacularly as cops chase a car
OL,14,     Gwith a familiar face.
OL,15,G1800FPolice Interceptors
OL,16,     GSteve rides to the aid of the
OL,17,     Garmed response team after reports
OL,18,     Gof a man drawing a gun on a pizza
OL,19,     Gdelivery driver. Charley and
OL,20,     GWayne take away a drink driver at
OL,21,     Gthe drive thru.
