OL,4,G0105FOutback Truckers
OL,5,     GOver the last three days, Steve
OL,6,     GGrahame has hauled 130 tonnes of
OL,7,     Gfreight a massive 2000 km, and
OL,8,     Ghis truck's taken a beating.
OL,9,     GUnder the bonnet the news isn't
OL,10,     Ggood.
OL,11,G0205FTrucking Hell
OL,12,     GIn Warwickshire Dave Crouch comes
OL,13,     Gto the rescue a tipper truck gets
OL,14,     Gstuck in deep mud on an isolated
OL,15,     Gfarm track. And a 26-ton truck
OL,16,     Gbreaks down beside the London Eye.
